reviewText: Very negative experience on this item with the seller "inspirations attic"  Had hoped it would be a nice gift to share some of my childhood with my kids, not the case.. still love marty thou.  by the way the whole series is free for amazon prime members
Product was exactly as described and packaging was perfect.
Exactly what I was looking for.
some of the videos weren't even opened, but one of the others had bad spots that didn't work

I love Marty Stouffer's work and we were very excited to have found this collection. But as it turns out the collection was poorly formatted and only about half of the episodes are watchable. We feel as if we have been cheated.
We are very pleased! They came very fast and were in very good condition! My husband and kids are very happy to have them!
